<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The A62 event is sent when an A61 (change consulting doctor) event is cancelled, either because of erroneous entry of the A61 event or because of a decision not to change the consulting physician(s) after all. <em>PV1-9 - Consulting Doctor</em> must show the patient&#8217;s doctor prior to the change being cancelled.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The fields included when this message is sent should be the fields pertinent to communicate this event. When other important fields change, it is recommended that the A08 (update patient information) event is used.</p>
</div>
